<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 36. Distribution map for Pampsilota afer, Pampsilota africanus, Pampsilota brandbergensis, and Pampsilota dahomeyanus." , "Figures 27 - 30. Pampsilota tsavoensis: 27. Valvulae 3 (lateral aspect); 28. Valvulae 3 (dorsal aspect); 29. Lancet; 30. Serrulae 10 - 11." , "Figure 26. Pampsilota nigeriae: Penis valve (left, lateral aspect)." , "Figures 45 - 50. Pampsilota brandbergensis ♂ (PT), dorsal / lateral. 47 - 50. Pampsilota dahomeyanus. 47 - 48. ♀, dorsal / lateral; 49 - 50. ♂, dorsal / lateral. Scale bars = 1 mm." , "Figures 15 - 19. Pampsilota dahomeyanus: 15. Valvulae 3 (lateral aspect); 16. Valvulae 3 (dorsal aspect); 17. Lancet; 18. Serrulae 10 - 11; 19. Penis valve (left, lateral aspect)." , "Figures 51 - 59. Pampsilota dahomeyanus, immature stages: 51. Mature larva, from L to R dorsal, lateral, ventral; 52. Young larva, lateral (preserved in ethanol); 53. Larvae on Lannea nigritana; 54. Metathoracic leg; 55. Head, frontal; 56. Eggs in base of leaflet. 57. Cocoons, from L to R with covering of sand, outer layer, inner layer; 58. Prepupa, from L to R ventral, lateral, dorsal; 59. Pupa, from L to R ventral, lateral, dorsal." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/118813" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/118793" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/118800" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/118811" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/118804" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/118798" .

